547
00:30:33,540 --> 00:30:36,710
如果我们被奇袭了  我不希望你还在外面
I don't want you there, out on the road, if we get blindsided.

548
00:30:37,570 --> 00:30:39,920
克莱尔  克莱尔
Claire? Claire.

549
00:30:44,160 --> 00:30:45,070
我这就回去
I'll come home.

550
00:30:45,480 --> 00:30:48,320
马上登机  就说你不舒服
You go straight to the plane. We'll say you weren't feeling well.

551
00:30:49,910 --> 00:30:50,740
好
Okay.

552
00:30:51,160 --> 00:30:55,480
上帝  让我平静接受我无法改变的事
God, grant me the serenity to accept the things I cannot change,

553
00:30:55,970 --> 00:30:58,320
让我勇敢改变我可以改变的事
the courage to change the things I can,

554
00:30:58,720 --> 00:31:00,830
并拥有分辨二者的智慧
and the wisdom to know the difference.

555
00:31:01,330 --> 00:31:04,510
坚持来  如果有帮助  就继续努力
Keep coming back. It works if you work it.

556
00:31:25,690 --> 00:31:26,470
怎么样
So?

557
00:31:27,440 --> 00:31:29,490
你还真以为他会喜欢这个吗
You honestly believed he'd go for this?

558
00:31:31,800 --> 00:31:32,580
是啊
Yeah.

559
00:31:33,320 --> 00:31:36,320
内容很好  而且很坦诚
The writing is good. And it's honest.

560
00:31:37,770 --> 00:31:39,430
但哪个神经正常的候选人
But what candidate in their right mind

561
00:31:39,430 --> 00:31:40,830
会希望这样的东西发表啊
would want something like this out there?

562
