I'm gonna finish it.

570
00:32:00,810 --> 00:32:02,710
如果有必要  我会改掉名字  当成小说
I'll change the names if I have to, call it fiction.

571
00:32:02,710 --> 00:32:04,960
他是美国总统
He's the President of the United States.

572
00:32:04,960 --> 00:32:06,640
-那又如何  -他能毁掉别人
- So what? - He crushes people.

573
