Let this go. Just start something new.

574
00:32:12,760 --> 00:32:14,170
"重新开始"
"Start something new."

575
00:32:16,040 --> 00:32:18,970
天呐  你根本不懂
Jesus... Christ, you don't get it.

576
00:32:20,340 --> 00:32:21,430
我经常这样
I do it all the time.

577
00:32:22,100 --> 00:32:24,600
我的编辑毙掉一篇报导  我继续做下一篇
My editor passes on a story, I move on to the next one.

578
00:32:24,600 --> 00:32:26,950
