I'm the one trying to save you from your own delusions.

581
00:32:31,670 --> 00:32:33,330
他就是这么说的
That's exactly what he said.

582
00:32:33,380 --> 00:32:34,570
也许他说得对
Maybe he's right.

583
00:32:42,180 --> 00:32:44,440
我都快对你有感情了
I almost felt something for you.

584
00:33:07,870 --> 00:33:08,610
进来吧
Come in.

585
00:33:15,240 --> 00:33:16,340
外套给我吧
Let me take your coat.

586
00:33:23,660 --> 00:33:25,160
要给你拿点什么吗  拿点喝的
Can I get you anything? Something to drink?

587
00:33:25,160 --> 00:33:27,180
不不  不用  谢谢
No. No, I'm good. Thanks.

588
00:33:36,770 --> 00:33:39,380
多谢你来我家  但我不会改变主意的
I appreciate the home visit, but I'm not gonna change my mind.

589
00:33:39,380 --> 00:33:41,460
不不  我没觉得你会改主意
No, no. I didn't think you would.

590
00:33:43,920 --> 00:33:44,880
出什么事了吗
Something wrong?

591
00:33:48,650 --> 00:33:49,850
我不知道该怎么做
I don't know what to do.

592
00:33:50,230 --> 00:33:51,630
我以为
I figured...

593
00:33:52,710 --> 00:33:54,610
我邀你加入竞选时
when I asked you to join the campaign,

594
00:33:54,610 --> 00:33:56,170
我以为你会答应
I just assumed you would say yes.

595
00:33:56,170 --> 00:33:58,320
我们就可以一起工作
That the two of us, we would be working together.

596
00:33:58,320 --> 00:33:59,210
而且
And...

597
00:34:04,960 --> 00:34:05,870
我...我
I... I...

598
00:34:06,620 --> 00:34:08,360
我无法停止想你
I can't stop thinking about you.

599
00:34:10,670 --> 00:34:11,960
你结婚了  杰姬
You're married, Jackie.

600
00:34:14,810 --> 00:34:16,370
因为错误的原因
For the wrong reasons.

601
00:34:18,590 --> 00:34:20,110
我以为你们彼此相爱
I thought you loved each other.

602
00:34:20,690 --> 00:34:21,770
不是这种爱
Not like this.

603
00:34:24,390 --> 00:34:26,150
我没做我想做的人
I'm not the person I want to be.

604
00:34:26,160 --> 00:34:29,720
你做了你应该做的  看看你的成就
You're who you need to be. Look at what you've achieved.

605
00:34:29,720 --> 00:34:31,920
但你做到了  你彻底放弃了
But you did it. You gave it all up.

606
00:34:31,940 --> 00:34:33,290
毫不犹豫
In a heartbeat.

607
00:34:39,040 --> 00:34:40,270
我们是不同的人
We're different people.

608
00:34:44,070 --> 00:34:45,060
你该走了
You should go.

609
00:34:48,450 --> 00:34:49,680
把这些抛在脑后
Put this behind you.

610
