看来以为我们依能保持亲密是我天真了
I guess it was naive to think that we could remain close.

611
00:35:18,480 --> 00:35:19,660
到此为止了吗
So this is it?

612
00:35:21,810 --> 00:35:23,760
是的  到此为止了
Yeah. It is.

613
00:35:30,050 --> 00:35:30,930
杰姬
Jackie?

614
00:35:35,080 --> 00:35:35,950
杰姬
Jackie...

615
00:36:21,620 --> 00:36:23,120
她说在她那儿
She says she has it.

616
00:36:24,100 --> 00:36:25,100
她撒谎
She doesn't.

617
00:36:27,550 --> 00:36:29,330
我怎么知道没有其它副本
How do I know there aren't other copies?

618
00:36:31,330 --> 00:36:32,810
你的烟放在哪
Where do you keep your cigarettes?

619
00:36:34,020 --> 00:36:35,520
在那上面的碗里
In the bowl up there.

620
00:37:28,660 --> 00:37:30,990
