有什么阻止了我  也许有一天我会用到
Something stopped me. Maybe I would need it one day.

623
00:37:37,840 --> 00:37:40,700
为了你  证明我的忠诚
For you. To prove my loyalty.

624
00:37:40,790 --> 00:37:43,650
你告诉她了  我可没法称之为忠诚
You told her. I'd hardly call that loyalty.

625
00:37:43,650 --> 00:37:44,930
我得向她表明我是认真的
I had to show her I was serious.

626
00:37:44,930 --> 00:37:46,620
这份日记就能证明
The journal was a way to do that.

627
00:37:47,600 --> 00:37:50,020
我从没想过把日记交给她
I never came close to putting it in her possession.

628
00:37:52,480 --> 00:37:54,070
我还要知道什么吗
Anything else I should know?

629
00:37:54,570 --> 00:37:57,100
我戒酒了  已经87天了
I'm sober. It's been 87 days.

630
00:37:57,100 --> 00:37:59,060
我是说关于邓巴
I meant in regards to Dunbar.

631
00:37:59,060 --> 00:38:01,980
这是有关的  现在双方势均力敌
It is related. This is a tight race.

632
00:38:03,680 --> 00:38:05,210
让我做你的幕僚长
Make me your Chief of Staff.

633
00:38:07,840 --> 00:38:08,850
你保证过的
You promised.

634
00:38:09,100 --> 00:38:11,580
你保证等我准备好了  这里会有我一席之地
You promised there'd be a place for me here when I was ready.

635
00:38:11,580 --> 00:38:13,440
那是在你旧瘾复发
That was before you fell off the wagon

636
00:38:13,440 --> 00:38:15,110
拿着日记走进来之前
and walked in here with that journal.

637
00:38:15,110 --> 00:38:16,350
我犯过错
I've made mistakes.

638
00:38:16,570 --> 00:38:17,730
我不止一次跌倒
I've fallen down more than once,

639
