A message from the president.

654
00:39:14,340 --> 00:39:16,410
我只有一件事要说
I have only one thing to say.

655
00:39:17,640 --> 00:39:19,340
去你妈的
Go fuck yourself.

656
00:39:24,780 --> 00:39:26,380
天呐  感觉太棒了
Christ, that felt good.

657
00:39:28,870 --> 00:39:30,450
