673
00:40:29,890 --> 00:40:30,900
我信他
I believe him.

674
00:40:33,560 --> 00:40:35,500
我要让他做幕僚长
And I'm gonna make him my Chief of Staff.

675
00:40:37,950 --> 00:40:39,290
你疯了吗
Are you out of your mind?

676
00:40:39,290 --> 00:40:41,640
我们需要他  克莱尔  如今更甚以往
We need him, Claire. We need him now more than ever.

677
00:40:41,640 --> 00:40:43,150
